RADIO BUTTONS and CHECK BOXES

Handling Checkboxes and RadioButtons

1. If you have only 1 checkbox or radiobutton = > just click on it
2. if you have multiple = >> store in a list and loop through

DropDowns

DD is menu or a method wihc allows a user to select one  or multiple options.

Type of DD:

1. Single select
2  Multiple select

Handling DD;
1. =>> just clicking on the DD adn click on the option // this way is not recommended to use
2. ==> using Select class // and this is the preferred way.
        in order ot use select class we need to make sure we have a <select> class
        we need to have <select> tag

before we interact we need to make sure we have select tag
Selecting options from the dropdown can be done in 3 ways:

3 ways to select options from DD:
1. by index
2. by visible text
3. by value

In order to deselect options we can use following methods -- Your DD must be a multi select DD
deselect is only available only for multiselect but not single select
deselectByValue();
deselectByIndex();
deselectByVisibleText();
deselectAll();

